{"id":900,"parent_id":890,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":900,"title":"Hosea 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hosea","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","Israel has plowed wickedness and reaped iniquity—Hosea calls upon Israel to seek the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.1","order":"02.29.010.60484"},["b","1"],"Israel",["i","is"],"an empty",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"vine"],", he bringeth forth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"fruit"],"unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"himself"],": according to the multitude of his fruit he hath increased the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"altars"],"; according to the goodness of his land they have made goodly images."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.2","order":"02.29.010.60485"},["b","2"],"Their heart is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"divided"],"; now shall they be found",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"faulty"],": he shall break down their altars, he shall spoil their images."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.3","order":"02.29.010.60486"},["b","3"],"For now they shall say, We have no king, because we feared not the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; what then should a king do to us?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.4","order":"02.29.010.60487"},["b","4"],"They have spoken words, swearing falsely in making a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"covenant"],": thus judgment springeth up as hemlock in the furrows of the field."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.5","order":"02.29.010.60488"},["b","5"],"The inhabitants of Samaria shall fear because of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"calves"],"of Beth-aven: for the people thereof shall mourn over it, and the priests thereof",["i","that"],"rejoiced on it, for the glory thereof, because it is departed from it."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.6","order":"02.29.010.60489"},["b","6"],"It shall be also carried unto Assyria",["i","for"],"a present to king",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Jareb"],": Ephraim shall receive",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"shame"],", and Israel shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"ashamed"],"of his own",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"counsel"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.7","order":"02.29.010.60490"},["b","7"],["i","As for"],"Samaria, her king is cut off as the foam upon the water."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.8","order":"02.29.010.60491"},["b","8"],"The high places also of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Aven"],", the sin of Israel, shall be destroyed: the thorn and the thistle shall come up on their altars; and they shall say to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"mountains"],", Cover us; and to the hills, Fall on us."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.9","order":"02.29.010.60492"},["b","9"],"O Israel, thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"sinned"],"from the days of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Gibeah"],": there they stood: the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"battle"],"in Gibeah against the children of iniquity did not overtake them."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.10","order":"02.29.010.60493"},["b","10"],["i","It is"],"in my desire that I should chastise them; and the people shall be gathered against them, when they shall bind themselves in their two furrows."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.11","order":"02.29.010.60494"},["b","11"],"And Ephraim",["i","is as"],"an heifer",["i","that is"],"taught,",["i","and"],"loveth to tread out",["i","the corn;"],"but I passed over upon her fair neck: I will make Ephraim to ride; Judah shall plow,",["i","and"],"Jacob shall break his clods."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.12","order":"02.29.010.60495"},["b","12"],"Sow to yourselves in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"righteousness"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"reap"],"in mercy;",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"break"],"up your fallow ground: for",["i","it is"],"time to seek the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", till he come and rain righteousness upon you."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.13","order":"02.29.010.60496"},["b","13"],"Ye have plowed",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"wickedness"],", ye have reaped iniquity; ye have eaten the fruit of lies: because thou didst trust in thy way, in the multitude of thy mighty men."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.14","order":"02.29.010.60497"},["b","14"],"Therefore shall a tumult arise among thy people, and all thy fortresses shall be spoiled, as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Shalman"],"spoiled Beth-arbel in the day of battle: the mother was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"dashed"],"in pieces upon",["i","her"],"children."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.15","order":"02.29.010.60498"},["b","15"],"So shall Beth-el do unto you because of your great wickedness: in a morning shall the king of Israel utterly be cut off."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.1a","order":"02.29.010.60499"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vineyard-of-the-lord"},"TG Vineyard of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.1b","order":"02.29.010.60501"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.32.1-77"},"Jacob 5:32 (1–77)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.1c","order":"02.29.010.60503"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/12.21.16-21"},"Luke 12:21 (16–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.1d","order":"02.29.010.60505"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/8.11"},"Hosea 8:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.2a","order":"02.29.010.60507"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/18.21"},"1 Kgs. 18:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/1.8"},"James 1:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/13.24"},"3 Ne. 13:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.2b","order":"02.29.010.60509"},["b","2b"],["span.small","HEB"],"guilty."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.4a","order":"02.29.010.60511"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/24.5"},"3 Ne. 24:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/104.5.4-5"},"D&C 104:5 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.5a","order":"02.29.010.60513"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/12.28"},"1 Kgs. 12:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.6a","order":"02.29.010.60515"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/5.13"},"Hosea 5:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.6b","order":"02.29.010.60517"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.6c","order":"02.29.010.60519"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.13"},"Jer. 48:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.6d","order":"02.29.010.60521"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/11.6.5-7"},"Hosea 11:6 (5–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.8a","order":"02.29.010.60523"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.15"},"Hosea 4:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.8b","order":"02.29.010.60525"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/23.30.26-33"},"Luke 23:30 (26–33)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.16.14-17"},"Rev. 6:16 (14–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.5"},"2 Ne. 26:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.14"},"Alma 12:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.9a","order":"02.29.010.60527"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/20.4.1-48"},"Judg. 20:4 (1–48)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.9b","order":"02.29.010.60529"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.9"},"Hosea 9:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.9c","order":"02.29.010.60531"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/20.19.18-21"},"Judg. 20:19 (18–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.12a","order":"02.29.010.60533"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.12b","order":"02.29.010.60535"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/harvest"},"TG Harvest"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.12c","order":"02.29.010.60537"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.3"},"Jer. 4:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.13a","order":"02.29.010.60539"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"TG Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.14a","order":"02.29.010.60541"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/17.3"},"2 Kgs. 17:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.14b","order":"02.29.010.60543"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.16.15-16"},"Hosea 13:16 (15–16)"],"."]]}
